cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.MA, cs.CV

The paper proposes a new approach for traffic signal control using reinforcement learning and graph convolutional networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.SY (Systems and Control). The paper also involves multi-agent reinforcement learning, which falls under cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems), and uses data from traffic cameras, which could be considered under cs.CV (Computer Vision).
